{"tid":2090730,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"救中大，評議會一定要去投票","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T06:27:35.000Z","uid":323643,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61b46feb9bd56e2d7a6154e30a19d36f5fd9294f","tid":2090730,"uid":323643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"建制已經騎劫中大多年，今次已經用書院力量洗橫手拉票。<br />\n<br />\n記住，非建制派的有要選主席的楊于銘，仲有常委盧俊宇，李軒朗。要投票啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n約兩星期後， 7月18日，星期六， 在中大校園舉行的&mdash;&mdash;中大校友評議會選舉，將會是中大歷史上最超人氣的一次 ！<br />\n<br />\n本來會議安排在「U拉」對面的「李兆基樓」一個會議室，以為好似以前一樣，最多咪得幾百人參加，但現在我睇，就算移師去有一千四百位的「邵逸夫堂」，也絕對迫爆，今次參加的校友可能有&mdash;&mdash;近萬人 ！<br />\n<br />\n點解無端端咁誇張？<br />\n<br />\n這個評議會其實權力有限， 但是很多「愛國老校友」， 一個月前已經出曬訊息， 話不要讓中大評議會&mdash;&mdash;「被別有用心的人操控」， 真係無中生有撩交打！<br />\n<br />\n根本都未開始準備選舉，就話人&mdash;&mdash;別有用心！<br />\n<br />\n這樣小小的一個評議會選舉，居然這班老嘢藍絲成立&mdash;&mdash;「競選辦」， 甚至本來準備有&mdash;&mdash;免費午餐聚會，實行拉委任票&mdash;&mdash;proxy飛 ，點知馬上有人話免費午餐，嘿嘿，有冇問題呀？ 於是唯有死死氣取消free lunch改為&mdash;&mdash;AA制，十分樣衰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍絲校友「競選辦」搞聚餐拉票，前一日的信息是費用全免（左圖），到第二日淆底了，馬上改成費用AA。<br />\n<br />\n出席拉票聚餐的校友為數不少。<br />\n這樣反而令其他大批校友反感，為什麼藍絲咁緊張這兩三個位？莫非是「上面」的動員令？於是反而令更多校友想出席這次會議，搞到中大準備改到邵逸夫堂開會，不過我估計肯定地方不夠，這是一次史上最人氣的中大校友選舉活動。<br />\n<br />\n你是中大校友，當然可以參加，要先登記，非常簡單，在網上download下面這張form， 填完電郵或Fax或寄去校友事務處即可，七月十日截止。<br />\n<br />\n無端端俾人話&mdash;&mdash;「別有用心」，你係中大人你都應該嬲！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31553/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%8F%8B%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-31553/%E4%BD%A0%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E5%AC%B2%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F31553%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-31553%2F%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E4%25BF%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E5%25AC%25B2%25EF%25BC%2581&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8AOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=28209140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/31553/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%8F%8B%E8%A9%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-31553/%E4%BD%A0%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A0%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E5%AC%B2%EF%BC%81</a>"},{"pid":"24b3a7b653d12ddf621891a8b2d725f509287b31","tid":2090730,"uid":255274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"推 中大人一定要投票"},{"pid":"6ee05c03e1606684c32bcb6426b12eee691aa83d","tid":2090730,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"92bc6d95033ddb4cafba25bdabc0ace8bbf488e4","tid":2090730,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac787e0e3f3d073eb7b44522b750ec136f9d936c","tid":2090730,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"［行動post］18/7中大投票師要人！全部同我10/7前登記！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077984\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077984</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b39dcbf2993883a9908ab33ed2056522fd86885d","tid":2090730,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5554c28f9e3b67dbc0c81251bab2eaa296fbca","tid":2090730,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3d567fa38920